fill bytes bytes: buffer of 4 u8 with value: u8 does:
  let i be 0
  while i is less than 4:
    bytes at i becomes value
    i becomes i plus 1

sum bytes bytes: buffer of 4 u8 gives i32:
  let total be 0
  let i be 0
  while i is less than 4:
    total becomes total plus (bytes at i as i32)
    i becomes i plus 1
  total

main gives i32:
  let bytes be buffer of 4 u8 filled with 0
  fill bytes bytes with 9
  sum bytes bytes
